  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832621782-QZ3XL5IHSBZDXDE0PX26/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Happy Friday, friends! In case you didn't know, I used to wear a tee shirt and jeans every single day. While I am still all about comfort, I want to take it up a notch and this outfit might just be the trick. The whole outfit is from <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=286192&amp;U=530666&amp;M=31374&amp;urllink=\">Cents of Style</a> and the super soft tunic is just <a href=\"http://shareasale.com/u.cfm?d=405095&amp;m=31374&amp;u=530666&amp;afftrack=\">$19.95 + FREE SHIPPING w/code TOPSTORY</a> through 3/26. I paired it with pants similar to <a href=\"https://www.mycentsofstyle.com/collections/bottoms/products/shannon-distressed-colored-pants\">these</a>, which have a bunch of holes in them but the colored denim make them feel fresh and fun for spring.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-Amy+Tangerine+_+Cents+of+Style+Tunic.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832657430-ISV5FDWP6NXDDC0LUGA0/7b-Amy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BCents%2Bof%2BStyle%2BTunic.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832657251-1RVD9N3YU6957TC471XF/7c-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832659584-K47M58CRCSGN913KAU9W/7d-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832659525-2RCTH5SV04GRUGQSU9EE/7e-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832660563-BU1VQJRX42B3668J5P17/7f-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832661340-E39S7SO2XR9RZZO58FNP/7g-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7h-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832661525-OQ2NS7H9YAGHJYRI5GTZ/7h-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7i-Cents+of+Style+x+Amy+Tangerine+_+Photos+by+Ann-Marie+Espinoza.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595832662517-BJEWRGEMKSO7RSGGH41C/7i-Cents%2Bof%2BStyle%2Bx%2BAmy%2BTangerine%2B_%2BPhotos%2Bby%2BAnn-Marie%2BEspinoza.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Location: <a href=\"https://www.tomdixon.net/\">TOM DIXON</a> at Platform LA | Photos by <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/\">Ann-Marie</a></p><p>So many sizes and colors available, I might have to stock up multiple colors of these babydoll tunics! Through 3/26 the tunics are just <a href=\"http://shareasale.com/u.cfm?d=405095&amp;m=31374&amp;u=530666&amp;afftrack=\">$19.95 + FREE SHIPPING w/code TOPSTORY</a>! </p>"
